txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: studded sword sheaths from the Angmarim infesting the ruined city of Annúminas. Deliver the items to Eirieniel at the Ranger-camp within Annúminas.
'We will drive these evil men from our city. This is proof that it will come to be.'
'The Angmarim are here in great force... we must do what we can to drive them back. Provide us proof, and we will see you well rewarded.'
Wardens of Annúminas Task: Studded Sword Sheaths
Eirieniel, a Ranger of Evendim located within Annúminas, awaits a delivery of studded sword sheaths at the camp there.
Deliver the studded sword sheaths to Eirieniel at the Ranger camp in Annúminas
You have accepted a task to collect studded sword sheaths from the Angmarim infesting the city of Annúminas and deliver them to Eirieniel at the Ranger-camp within the city.
Wanted: studded sword sheaths from the Angmarim infesting the ruined city of Annúminas.
